      "span_text": "Chang et al. [CITATION_1] operated on 63 children between the ages of one and three years, using the technique described by Salter, and found 30 cases of avascular necrosis: 16 cases with early signs of this, within the first two years after the operation, and 14 with signs seen later on after the operation."
